1. Purpose

This document defines the contract between:

The Halisako Experience Timeline (HXT) generated by upstream intelligence engines.

and

The Halisako Cinematic Experience (HCE) generated by the Cinematic Engine.

The contract ensures that analytical game events can be consistently transformed into cinematic scenes regardless of the final rendering technology.

